Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Add 6 SOSTAC® methodology skills as system defaults (S1/O/S2/T/A/C)
  each with full methodology knowledge in prompt field
- Add isActive field to Skill type for enable/disable toggle
- Add toggleDefaultSkill() and getActiveSkills() to skill-store
- Enhance discussion-engine with buildSkillContext() to inject
  methodology knowledge when prompt > 100 chars
- Update skills page with stats cards, search, filter (all/active/SOSTAC/custom)
- Update skill-card with toggle button and SOSTAC badge
- Meeting creation now only shows active skills

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
